---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Workflow Automation — Nexus AI"
  description="Nexus AI's workflow automation services eliminate manual drudgery with intelligent process automation — no-code and custom solutions for CRM, ERP, document processing, and data pipelines."
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-900 via-brand-800 to-brand-950 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-warm-300">Workflow Automation</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          Workflow Automation<br />
          <span class="text-warm-300">That Actually Works</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-warm-200">
          Stop spending your team's time on repetitive, manual processes. We build automation 
          that connects your tools, processes your documents, and executes your workflows — 
          reliably, at scale, and without breaking your stack.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a
href="/nexus-ai/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/25 hover:bg-brand-400 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 active:scale-[0.97]"
          >
            Start Your Automation Journey
            <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Offer -->
    <section class="bg-white px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-600">What We Offer</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-4xl">
            No-Code Speed. Custom Precision.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
            We believe the best automation strategy is the one that actually gets adopted. That's why 
            we meet you where you are — whether your team prefers visual workflow builders or needs 
            deeply integrated custom pipelines.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- No-Code Approach -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink">No-Code Automation</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
              Perfect for operations teams and department-level workflows. Using tools like n8n and 
              Make, we build visual automation pipelines that your team can understand, modify, 
              and extend without writing a single line of code. Deployment in days, not months.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Custom Automation -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Custom Automation Engineering</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
              For complex, mission-critical workflows that demand more than off-the-shelf connectors. 
              We write custom Python middleware, build API integrations with legacy ERP systems, 
              and design fault-tolerant data pipelines that handle millions of events per day.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Automation Types -->
    <section class="bg-surface px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-600">Automation Types</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-4xl">
            Automate Every Corner of Your Business
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
            From customer-facing workflows to back-office operations — we cover the full spectrum 
            of enterprise automation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <!-- CRM Automation -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100 group-hover:bg-warm-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">CRM Automation</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
              Automate lead capture, contact enrichment, follow-up sequences, and deal-stage updates. 
              Integrate Salesforce, HubSpot, or Zoho with your email, calendar, and Slack — so your 
              sales team never drops a ball.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- ERP Integration -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100 group-hover:bg-warm-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">ERP Integration</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
              Connect SAP, Oracle, NetSuite, or Microsoft Dynamics with your modern SaaS stack. 
              Automate PO-to-payment workflows, inventory synchronization, order-to-cash cycles, 
              and inter-system data reconciliation without manual intervention.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Document Processing -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100 group-hover:bg-warm-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Document Processing</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
              Turn unstructured documents into structured data. Our pipeline combines OCR, LLM-based 
              extraction, and rule-based validation to handle invoices, contracts, insurance claims, 
              and regulatory filings at enterprise scale with 99%+ extraction accuracy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Data Pipelines -->
          <div class="group rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100 group-hover:bg-warm-200 transition-colors">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5m.75-9l3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0116.5 7.605" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Data Pipelines</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
              Build reliable ETL/ELT pipelines that move and transform data across databases, APIs, 
              and data warehouses. Our pipelines include built-in error handling, retry logic, 
              monitoring, and alerting — so your data is always fresh and trustworthy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tech Stack -->
    <section class="bg-white px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-600">Our Tech Stack</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-4xl">
            Battle-Tested Tools, Expertly Applied
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
            We don't lock you into a single platform. We choose the right tool for each job — 
            and we're fluent in all of them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-4">
          <!-- n8n -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-700">n8n</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-ink">n8n</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">Self-hosted workflow automation with 400+ integrations</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Make -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-700">Make</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-ink">Make</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">Visual no-code automation for business teams</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Python -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-700">Py</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-ink">Python</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">Custom middleware, data pipelines, and API glue code</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Zapier -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent-200 hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-warm-100">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-700">Zap</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-ink">Zapier</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">Quick-start automation for SaaS-to-SaaS connections</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process: Discovery → Design → Implement → Monitor -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-900 via-brand-800 to-brand-950 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-warm-300">Our Process</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
            From Discovery to Continuous Optimization
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-warm-200">
            We follow a proven four-phase methodology that de-risks automation and ensures 
            every workflow delivers measurable business impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <!-- Discovery -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600/30 border-2 border-brand-400">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">01</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Discovery</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-warm-200">
              We map every step of your current workflow, interview stakeholders, and analyze 
              system logs to identify bottlenecks, handoffs, and high-ROI automation opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Design -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600/30 border-2 border-brand-400">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">02</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Design</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-warm-200">
              We architect the automation solution — choosing the right tools, designing the data 
              flow, defining error handling, and building a prototype that you can test and validate.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Implement -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600/30 border-2 border-brand-400">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">03</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Implement</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-warm-200">
              We deploy the automation into production with phased rollout, comprehensive testing, 
              staff training, and parallel-run validation to ensure zero disruption to your business.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Monitor -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600/30 border-2 border-brand-400">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">04</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Monitor</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-warm-200">
              We provide ongoing monitoring, alerting, and optimization. Our dashboards track 
              every workflow's performance, and we proactively refine automations as your business evolves.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <section class="bg-white px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-600">Use Cases</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-4xl">
            Real Scenarios, Real Impact
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">
            Here's how workflow automation has transformed operations for companies like yours.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 space-y-10">
          <!-- Use Case 1 -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-5 items-center rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 lg:p-10">
            <div class="lg:col-span-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-warm-100 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-700">Accounts Payable</span>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-ink">Invoice-to-Payment Automation</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
                A mid-market manufacturing firm was processing 8,000 invoices monthly through a 
                manual three-approval workflow that took an average of 14 days per invoice. We 
                deployed an automated pipeline that extracts invoice data using AI, matches it 
                against PO and receipt records, routes exceptions to the right approver, and 
                triggers payment in the ERP — all within 90 minutes. The result: processing time 
                dropped from 14 days to 2 hours, late payment penalties were eliminated, and the 
                AP team reallocated 70% of their time to strategic supplier management.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700">98% reduction in invoice processing time</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 lg:pl-8">
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-50 to-warm-100 p-6">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-700">Before</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-ink">14 days</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">per invoice cycle</p>
                <div class="mt-4 h-px bg-warm-200"></div>
                <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-brand-700">After</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700">2 hours</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">per invoice cycle</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Use Case 2 -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-5 items-center rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 lg:p-10">
            <div class="lg:col-span-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-warm-100 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-700">Sales Operations</span>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-ink">Automated Lead-to-Opportunity Pipeline</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
                A B2B SaaS company was losing 40% of inbound leads because manual qualification 
                and routing took 6+ hours. We built an automation that captures leads from web forms, 
                chat, and email, enriches them with firmographic data from Clearbit, scores them 
                using a custom lead scoring model, and routes qualified leads to the right sales rep 
                via Slack — all within 60 seconds. The result: lead response time dropped from hours 
                to under a minute, and the sales team converted 3.2x more leads in the first quarter.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700">3.2x lead conversion improvement</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 lg:pl-8">
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-50 to-warm-100 p-6">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-700">Before</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-ink">6+ hours</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">lead response time</p>
                <div class="mt-4 h-px bg-warm-200"></div>
                <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-brand-700">After</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700">&lt; 60 sec</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">lead response time</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Use Case 3 -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-5 items-center rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 lg:p-10">
            <div class="lg:col-span-3">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-warm-100 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-700">HR & Onboarding</span>
              <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-ink">Employee Onboarding Automation</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
                A fast-growing fintech company was hiring 30+ employees per month, and each new 
                hire required 18 manual tasks across HRIS, IT, payroll, Slack, email, and facility 
                management. The manual process took each new hire an average of 3 days to get fully 
                set up — and errors (missing accounts, wrong permissions) were common. We deployed a 
                multi-step automation that triggers the moment an offer is accepted: creates accounts, 
                provisions tools, assigns training modules, sends welcome emails, and notifies the 
                team — all within 15 minutes. New hire time-to-productivity dropped from 5 days to 1.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700">80% faster employee onboarding</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 lg:pl-8">
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-50 to-warm-100 p-6">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-700">Before</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-ink">3 days</p>
